folder: Atlantic Avenue & Warwick Street, Brooklyn, NY
text:
(1)
Atlantic Ave., east from and including Warwick Street. The view shows the Warwick Street Station of the Long Island Railroad.
July 27, 1930.
P. L. Sperr.

(2)
The same, from a slightly different angle.
July 27, 1930.
